==制作==
===开发===
2017年2月，消息指[[瑪嘉·莎塔碧|瑪嘉·莎塔碧]]将指导[[玛丽·居里|玛丽·居里]]的传记片，[[频道制片公司|频道制片公司]]和[[Working_Title_Films|Working Title Films]]参与制作，初步预计于“2017年秋季”开始制作<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2017/02/marjane-satrapi-jack-thorne-radioactive-marie-curie-working-title-studiocanal-1201913575/|title=Marjane Satrapi To Helm 'Radioactive' Marie Curie Story For Working Title & Studiocanal|last=Tartaglione|first=Nancy|last2=Tartaglione|first2=Nancy|date=2017-02-16|website=Deadline Hollywood|access-date=2019-10-16|archive-date=2019-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191019065715/https://deadline.com/2017/02/marjane-satrapi-jack-thorne-radioactive-marie-curie-working-title-studiocanal-1201913575/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2017年5月[[戛纳电影节|戛纳电影节]]期间，[[裴淳华|裴淳华]]出演居里夫人<ref>{{cite web|url=https://variety.com/2017/film/festivals/cannes-film-festival-2017-rosamund-pike-marie-curie-1202428403/|title=Rosamund Pike Set for Marie Curie Story 'Radioactive' From Working Title, Studiocanal (EXCLUSIVE)|last1=Hopewell|first1=John|last2=Keslassy|first2=Elsa|date=2017-05-16|work=Variety|access-date=2019-10-16|archive-date=2019-10-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191010114149/https://variety.com/2017/film/festivals/cannes-film-festival-2017-rosamund-pike-marie-curie-1202428403/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===拍摄===
2018年2月，{{tsl|en|Amazon Studios|亚马逊工作室}}购得影片美国地区发行权，同时影片开始在匈牙利[[布达佩斯|布达佩斯]]和[[埃斯泰尔戈姆|埃斯泰尔戈姆]]取景<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.szeretgom.hu/content/86721-varsova-valtozott-a-vizivaros |title=Varsóvá változott a Víziváros |website=Szeretgom.hu |language=hu |date=2018-02-19 |accessdate=2020-10-06 |archive-date=2019-06-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190617051947/https://www.szeretgom.hu/content/86721-varsova-valtozott-a-vizivaros |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Keslassy |first=Elsa |url=https://variety.com/2018/film/global/amazon-marjane-astrapi-radioactive-marie-curie-biopic-1202704419/ |title=Amazon Boards Marjane Satrapi's Marie Curie Biopic 'Radioactive' (EXCLUSIVE) |work=Variety |date=2018-02-19 |accessdate=2020-10-06 |archive-date=2019-08-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190809145812/https://variety.com/2018/film/global/amazon-marjane-astrapi-radioactive-marie-curie-biopic-1202704419/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。随后几天，演员[[山姆·萊利|山姆·萊利]]、[[安雅·泰勒-喬伊|安雅·泰勒-喬伊]]、[[阿奈林·巴納德|阿奈林·巴納德]]和{{tsl|en|Simon Russell Beale|西蒙·罗素·比尔}}宣布加入剧组<ref>{{cite web |last=Roxborough |first=Scott |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/berlin-sam-riley-anya-taylor-joy-aneurin-barnard-join-marie-curie-biopic-radioactive-1087338 |title=Berlin: Sam Riley, Anya Taylor-Joy, Aneurin Barnard Join Marie Curie Biopic 'Radioactive' |work=The Hollywood Reporter |date=2018-02-22 |accessdate=2020-10-06 |archive-date=2020-09-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200917060852/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/berlin-sam-riley-anya-taylor-joy-aneurin-barnard-join-marie-curie-biopic-radioactive-1087338 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

