.filmstories.co.uk/news/radioactive-heads-to-digital-download-next-month/ |title=Radioactive heads to digital download next month |website=Film Stories |date=2020-05-19 |accessdate=2020-07-26 |archive-date=2020-07-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200726231705/https://www.filmstories.co.uk/news/radioactive-heads-to-digital-download-next-month/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。最终，影片于2020年6月15日通过数字平台在英国发行，7月6日登陆[[隨選視訊|隨選視訊]]服务，7月27日发行DVD<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.studiocanalpress.co.uk/press/single/1985 |title=Radioactive – Press Assets |publisher=StudioCanal UK |accessdate=2020-07-23 |archive-date=2020-07-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200724085300/http://www.studiocanalpress.co.uk/press/single/1985 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在美国，影片原定于2020年4月24日由亚马逊工作室在剧院发行<ref>{{cite web |last=Rosser |first=Michael |url=https://www.screendaily.com/news/radioactive-director-marjane-satrapi-reveals-why-she-chooses-not-to-work-with-us-producers/5147926.article |title='Radioactive' director Marjane Satrapi reveals why she chooses not to work with US producers |website={{tsl|en|Screen Daily||Screen Daily}} |date=2020-03-09 |accessdate=2020-07-11 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200711052545/https://www.screendaily.com/news/radioactive-director-marjane-satrapi-reveals-why-she-chooses-not-to-work-with-us-producers/5147926.article |archivedate=2020-07-11 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，后改为7月24日登陆[[亞馬遜影片|亞馬遜影片]]<ref>{{cite web |last=Aquilina |first=Tyler |url=https://ew.com/movies/rosamund-pike-radioactive-marie-curie-biopic-trailer/ |title=Rosamund Pike is ''Radioactive'' asMarie Curie in new biopic trailer |work=Entertainment Weekly |date=2020-07-10 |accessdate=2020-07-11 |archive-date=2020-07-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200711040335/https://ew.com/movies/rosamund-pike-radioactive-marie-curie-biopic-trailer/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==评价==
===专业评价===
汇总媒体[[烂番茄|烂番茄]]评论131条，新鲜度61%，平均得分6.02/10。网站共识认为：“《以光之名》的剧本存在缺陷，剧情选择起反作用，但两者都被裴淳华真诚致敬一位杰出科学家的精彩表现抵消<ref name="RT">{{cite web |url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/radioactive |title=''Radioactive'' (2019) |website=Rotten Tomatoes |accessdate=2020-08-22 |archive-date=2020-08-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200821085944/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/radioactive |dead-url=no }}</ref>。”[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]评论31条，平均分56/100，表示“褒贬不一或口碑平平”<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.metacritic.com/movie/radioactive |title=''Radioactive'' Reviews |website=Metacritic |accessdate=2020-08-08 |archive-date=2020-07-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200726025946/https://www.metacritic.com/movie/radioactive |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

